WHATâ€™S AT PLAY?
Escape the BOOM! is a cooperative game. One player must defuse the bomb but has no idea how. The rest of the team has the manual with the necessary instructions but cannot see the bomb. The only way to succeed? Communication! And lots of it. You have only five minutes to decipher the clues together. Withstand the pressure, keep your coolâ€¦ and Escape the BOOM!
WHO IS IT FOR?
Whether youâ€™re fans of live escape games, challenging puzzles, or have a history of defusing bombs, Escape the BOOM! will keep you on the edge of your seat. You can play Escape the BOOM! together around a table, but itâ€™s also perfect for remote gaming via Zoom, Teams, or Discord.
